      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, known for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via the M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the dual-VANOS system is quiet, rod bearings have been addressed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry, offering the precise turn-in and communicative feedback the chassis is famous for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain synchronization remain sharp, making this a premier candidate for the purist driver.",
